{"tid":1598334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"恭賀！37歲瀧澤秀明成傑尼斯副社長","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T13:17:45.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fe270647861c09bee7b031a0c88d64170cc0a2d6","tid":1598334,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8u060M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8u060M.png&h=26399e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日媒《日刊體育》今（27）報導，傑尼斯下午正式發布消息，由瑪麗喜多川就任會長、喜多川姪女藤島茱莉景子就任社長，而瀧澤秀明則成為傑尼斯的副社長，不過有網友對此表示：「就算瀧澤秀明來，也救不了傑尼斯。」<br />\n <br />\n37歲的瀧澤秀明為前傑尼斯偶像，如今退出幕前，專注幕後工作，日劇《孤高的手術刀》則為他的連續劇告別作。<br />\n <br />\n由於傑尼斯事務所創辦人Johnny喜多川日前因病逝世，當時瀧澤秀明任輔助，持續培養小傑尼斯與發掘新人，今發布訊息後，不少人也對三人能否延續龐大的偶像帝國，成為未來注目焦點。"},{"pid":"7bac25c7dc1a1f5923ca5314defbfdcf7429507a","tid":1598334,"uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"以前細個TVB播嗰一套新聞女郎有佢，嗰陣覺得佢都幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b73440be703b343fd5bee2837aca14242d26243","tid":1598334,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013585728edc6e9594344601dd6e0822f82a5efb","tid":1598334,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bac25c7dc1a1f5923ca5314defbfdcf7429507a","tid":1598334,"uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"以前細個TVB播嗰一套新聞女郎有佢，嗰陣覺得佢都幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:39:44.000Z","msg":"義經<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc9e3d9b011954c5aff8f38604509923e5619d2","tid":1598334,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dis